text.tspan: Historical trade openness in Europe, 1815 to 1949

Sum of exports and imports of goods and services, divided by
gross domestic product
(GDP), expressed as a
percentage. This is also known as the "trade openness index".
Data source: International Historical Statistics - Brian Mitchell (2015)
